{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s006", "order": 6, "text": "**Rollout:**", "char_start": 555, "char_end": 567, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 3}
{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s007", "order": 7, "text": "Deployment will be controlled via the feature flag `risk_threshold_v2`.", "char_start": 570, "char_end": 641, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 12}
{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s008", "order": 8, "text": "The rollout will follow a staged deployment strategy, starting at 10% of the user base, scaling progressively to 100% over five days as follows:", "char_start": 642, "char_end": 786, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 29}
{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s009", "order": 9, "text": "- **Day 1:** 10%  \n- **Day 2:** 25%  \n- **Day 3:** 50%  \n- **Day 4:** 75%  \n- **Day 5:** 100%", "char_start": 788, "char_end": 881, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 37}
{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s010", "order": 10, "text": "Daily monitoring will ensure stability and threshold efficacy before proceeding to each subsequent phase.", "char_start": 885, "char_end": 990, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 15}
{"doc_id": "7b325d24-7f7e-55a2-8bba-ab010bbb5209", "req_id": "REQ-048", "sent_id": "REQ-048::s011", "order": 11, "text": "**Audit:**", "char_start": 992, "char_end": 1002, "splitter": "stanza", "token_count": 3}
